??? summary "ebreak  (Environment Breakpoint). $\fbox{rv_i}$"

    RaiseException(Breakpoint).

    Make a request of the debugger by raising a Breakpoint exception.

??? summary "ecall  (Environment Call). $\fbox{rv_i}$"

    RaiseException(EnvironmentCall).

    Make a request of the execution environment by raising an Environment Call exception.
